import classes from './Layout.module.css'
import Navigation from './Navigation'
import { Fragment } from "react"

const Layout = (props)=>{
    return<Fragment>
        <Navigation/>
        <main className={classes.main}>{props.children}</main>
    </Fragment>
}
export default Layout
